restlib.data

Class EntityTag

  • java.lang.Object
    • restlib.data.EntityTag
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    EntityTag.Strong, EntityTag.Weak

    @Immutable
public abstract class EntityTag
extends Object
    An opaque validator for differentiating between multiple representations of the same resource, regardless of whether those multiple representations are due to resource state changes over time, content negotiation resulting in multiple representations being valid at the same time, or both.
